Package: Wayfarer
Type: Package
Title: Multi-scale spatial binning analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lambda", "Moses", email = "dl3764@columbia.edu", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7092-9427"))
  )
Description: This package performs spatial binning at different resolutions and
    compares Voyager spatial analysis results across the resolutions. Plotting
    functions across resolutions are implemented. Linear mixed models are used
    to compare across biological conditions when there are multiple samples per
    condition.
